(109, 56, 'faq_0_faq_a', 'A: Yes, we are insured. In the event of damage, we will repair your furniture if possible. If the damaged piece is not repairable, we will pay the depreciated value of the damaged piece.'),
(110, 56, '_faq_0_faq_a', 'field_587557281b82b'),
(111, 56, 'faq_1_faq_q', 'Q: Are your movers full-time employees with experience?'),
(112, 56, '_faq_1_faq_q', 'field_587557171b82a'),
(113, 56, 'faq_1_faq_a', 'A: Yes. Many of our movers have been with us for years and our new hire criteria include professional moving experience. We are also committed to continuous training for our employees.'),
(114, 56, '_faq_1_faq_a', 'field_587557281b82b'),
(115, 56, 'faq_2_faq_q', 'Q: How do I know youre not one of those unscrupulous residential moving companies that you see on the news that quote one price and then charge another, or damages furniture and doesnt fix it?'),
(116, 56, '_faq_2_faq_q', 'field_587557171b82a'),
(117, 56, 'faq_2_faq_a', 'A: Austin Moving Forward is fully licensed and insured. We also have a massive collection of great testimonials from many of our satisfied customers. To read your consumer rights and responsibilities, look up important information about our company, or research any moving company visit protectyourmove.gov'),
(118, 56, '_faq_2_faq_a', 'field_587557281b82b'),
